						<outline text="LATAM -- June 15, 9:30AM ET"/>
						<outline text="EMEA -- June 16, 4:30AM ET"/>
						<outline text="North America -- June 17, 11:30AM ET"/>
						</outline>
					<outline text="The only hard ones to figure out were the APAC times, which are in &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.timeanddate.com/time/zones/sgt&quot;&gt;SGT&lt;/a&gt;, which is 12 hours ahead of Eastern time." created="Tue, 18 May 2021 19:50:01 GMT"/>
